#: ../../storage.rst:2
msgid "存储与结果访问"
msgstr "Storage and Result Access"

#: ../../storage.rst:4
msgid "AgentSociety 2 把实验数据落到两个位置："
msgstr "AgentSociety 2 stores experiment data in two places:"

#: ../../storage.rst:6
msgid ""
"**SQLite 数据库**: ``<run_dir>/sqlite.db``。所有 replay 数据（agent profile、agent "
"快照、env 快照、事件流等）都写入这一个数据库，并通过 catalog 表自描述。"
msgstr ""
"**SQLite database**: ``<run_dir>/sqlite.db``. All replay data, including "
"agent profiles, agent snapshots, environment snapshots, and event "
"streams, is written into this single database and described through "
"catalog tables."

#: ../../storage.rst:7
msgid ""
"**本地工作目录**: "
"``<run_dir>/artifacts/``、``<run_dir>/agents/agent_<id>/``、``<run_dir>/pid.json``"
" 等文件，存放 ``ask``/``intervene`` 产物、agent workspace 与运行时元信息。"
msgstr ""
"**Local working directory**: files such as ``<run_dir>/artifacts/``, "
"``<run_dir>/agents/agent_<id>/``, and ``<run_dir>/pid.json``, which store"
" ``ask``/``intervene`` artifacts, agent workspaces, and runtime metadata."

